description: The aim of the Project is the rehabilitation of destroeyd three bridges in the middle area of Gaza Strip with total budget of US$ 985,872 provided by the Government of Brazil.

subproject.corporate outcome: Expansion and access to financial services for the poor, employment and income generation and access to markets, goods and services.
subproject.description: Construction and rehabilitation of three bridges which connect 5 towns located along Wadi Gaza at both sides of the Wadi in the middle area of Gaza Strip. These bridges are Al Sikka bridge, Wadi Gaza bridge and Al Zahra box culvert. The project will create around 10,000 workdays.
subproject.title: Rehab. of Destroyed Bridges

title: Rehabilitation of Destroyed Bridges in the Gaza Strip
